22926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T06:07:32.000Z","msg":"不嬲香港人係大陸當係「外國人」啦<br />\n租酒店、揸車都係當你係外國人<br />\n咩國民身分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T06:09:49.000Z","msg":"共產黨就係咁<br />\n拎你著數就話大家係同胞<br />\n唔想益你就係境外人士"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T06:39:13.000Z","msg":"點止<br />\n入咗WTO又唔跟規矩, 對住歐美大玩保護主義攞盡著數<br />\n侵加佢關稅就批評美國破壞自由貿易, 仲呼籲歐盟國同佢一齊對抗美國<br />\n醜撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T06:48:53.000Z","msg":"唔洗講出來，由得支那繼續做國際小丑"},{"pid":"29c8b0109ca89f6f59251e4a6f730e341f5711b3","tid":626354,"uid":172497,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T06:50:49.000Z","msg":"澳門狗平時咁愛國，請問宜家點睇？"},{"pid":"fc4f61f358d5092c1341d164d30d99bbd58280ab","tid":626354,"uid":78440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a00db7abcffb8774ec5d1259633a1e2673f9ec3e","tid":626354,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T04:51:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180412/s00001/2f5be7dfc2c19091291d7fa5497ae93d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180412%2Fs00001%2F2f5be7dfc2c19091291d7fa5497ae93d.jpg&h=3bcf87b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n回歸後港人身分認同問題一直備受關注，而立法會議員謝偉俊接獲投訴，指內地海南省「海南文昌航天發射場」把港人及台灣人定為「境外人士」，列明「 謝絕參觀」，謝偉俊亦在facebook感嘆「中港融合障礙」、「港人身分認同危機」。<br />\n<br />\n謝偉俊昨於fb以&lt;【港人與?不得進入】&gt;為題發帖，指街坊投訴過年到海南省旅遊，本打算參觀「海南文昌航天發射場」，卻被禁止入內參觀，原來售票處旁懸掛了告示牌，把港人及台灣人列作「境外人士」，表明「謝絕參觀」，令街坊大惑不解。謝偉俊並標籤了「#中港融合障礙」、「#港人身分認同危機」及「#拒諸門外」等。<br />\n<br />\n網民都對此大感不解，質疑做法不合理，「香港人為境外人士？」、「 唔合理，唔畀外國人參觀都理解，港澳同胞都唔得？有違統一嘅本意」。<br />\n<br />\n謝偉俊就事件詢問商務及經濟發展局，局長邱騰華書面回覆指，「海南文昌航天發射場」的接待設施和條件仍在「建設」和「完善」中，暫時無法承載大量訪客，故現階段未開放予港澳台及國際人士。<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華又說，港府會繼續向內地反映港人意見，爭取更多便利港人到內地旅遊及發展政策，「把握國家發展帶來的機遇，提升港人對國家的認同感」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180412/s00001/1523503650538\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180412%2Fs00001%2F1523503650538&d=Dt7%2BsZKySRTPXTrBALTzW%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=b26e1d81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180412%2Fs00001%2F1523503650538&h=30c6c976\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180412/s00001/1523503650538</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T07:03:46.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"00d1b06c9ba9a0e5147f728b0df28a9620390665","tid":626354,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73fb96a0aa2eeccba72bbfe56a68d81b55401492","tid":626354,"uid":158613,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T04:53:21.000Z","msg":"香港人唔可以做解放軍，點睇?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T07:11:52.000Z","msg":"香港人唔可以做解放軍 = 外國人唔可以做解放軍"},{"pid":"821c3d1a2e1c08829ab1767fb3e04b1fbc660c4b","tid":626354,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9731b4f866022d5d5a11038c75b919b4eb7962a","tid":626354,"uid":41500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T05:43:34.000Z","msg":"CNO <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T07:13:15.000Z","msg":"中國公民（境外）"},{"pid":"afe2904da3df75237a6b4d0a3fa407f884bcd789","tid":626354,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T07:15:39.000Z","msg":"發現新大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ee355fdf4eb99b31031294b6c5b587b66e4bad","tid":626354,"uid":52056,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"250b545dc0b9879dc583a6dd0098792f60c0b8f1","tid":626354,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b7884c3465af619f2dea9725d90c9dc9e665b10","tid":626354,"uid":22701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quo